    FTP offers six different prop models, ranging from instant funding to one step and two step challenges. You can choose between trailing or static drawdown models, depending on how you prefer risk to be calculated, and each program comes with different profit targets, loss limits, and payout structures.
  </p>

  <!-- Per-challenge summaries -->
  <div class="space-y-3 mb-8">
    <div class="rounded-lg bg-slate-50 border border-slate-200 p-4">
      <p class="font-bold text-slate-900 mb-1">Master – Instant Funding</p>
      <p>No evaluation or profit targets, but the strictest risk rules with tight trailing drawdown limits. Account sizes from $5,000 to $100,000.</p>
      <p class="text-xs text-teal-600 font-semibold mt-1">Skip the evaluation entirely and start trading immediately</p>
    </div>
    <div class="rounded-lg bg-slate-50 border border-slate-200 p-4">
      <p class="font-bold text-slate-900 mb-1">Experienced – 1 Step Challenge</p>
      <p>A one step challenge with trailing drawdown and a single 10% profit target. Account sizes from $12,500 to $200,000. FTP's most popular option.</p>
