    </div>
    <div class="rounded-lg bg-slate-50 border border-slate-200 p-4">
      <p class="font-bold text-slate-900 mb-1">Advanced – 2 Step (Trailing Drawdown)</p>
      <p>Traditional two step structure with 10% and 5% profit targets. More relaxed drawdown rules with 5% daily trailing and 10% max trailing.</p>
      <p class="text-xs text-teal-600 font-semibold mt-1">Best suited for swing traders or higher timeframe strategies</p>
    </div>
    <div class="rounded-lg bg-slate-50 border border-slate-200 p-4">
      <p class="font-bold text-slate-900 mb-1">Premium – 2 Step (Trailing Drawdown)</p>
      <p>Lower profit targets of 8% and 5% but tighter drawdown limits of 4% daily and 8% max trailing. Requires 3 minimum profitable trading days.</p>
      <p class="text-xs text-teal-600 font-semibold mt-1">For traders who prioritise lower targets over drawdown flexibility</p>
    </div>
    <div class="rounded-lg bg-slate-50 border border-slate-200 p-4">
      <p class="font-bold text-slate-900 mb-1">Prestige Lite – 2 Step (Static Drawdown)</p>
      <p>Fixed drawdown model with 6% profit targets in both steps, 3% daily and 6% overall static loss limits. Lower 80% profit split.</p>
      <p class="text-xs text-teal-600 font-semibold mt-1">For traders who dislike trailing drawdown and prefer known risk limits</p>
